	<entry name="VossPatternLasgun" value="Voss Pattern Lasgun"/>
	<entry name="VossPatternLasgunFlavor" value="The M35 Galaxy Pattern Lasgun was designed to complement its cousin the Kantrael by being smaller and more able to sustain fire, and it has mainly been adopted by the Catachan Jungle Fighters and Armageddon Steel Legion. Furthermore, it's modular, with the main point of interest being the barrel, allowing it to be easily turned into a long-las or Voss Pattern Lasgun. The Voss Pattern has an even shorter barrel and typically is paired with a foldable wire stock, limiting range but making easier to fit inside an APC, which is exactly what the Steel Legion needs."/>
	<entry name="OrkHuntersTrap" value="Punji Trap"/>
	<entry name="OrkHuntersTrapDescription" value="Slows and damages enemy infantry."/>
	<entry name="OrkHuntersTrapFlavor" value="Armageddon Ork Hunters deftly lay pitfall traps to halt any would-be attackers. Da Boyz aren't so tough with broken legs and half of them impaled."/>
