	<entry name="uwu_SteelLegion_DiposableMissile_TEMPLATE" value="Disposable Missile Launcher"/>
	<entry name="uwu_SteelLegion_DiposableMissile_TEMPLATEFlavor" value="Missile launchers have great destructive power, but they are limited by their clunkiness. Firing multiple shots requires setup time, ideally with a loader assisting. However, sometimes a single volley of missiles is all that's needed. The Mechanicus of Armageddon hold the designs for a single-use missile launcher, held in a collapsible tuble. It is unknown what significance the original text &quot;Em 72 Lambda Alpha W&quot; holds, but it has been dubbed the &quot;LOH&quot; after archmagos Lambda-0H."/>
